           TO ANOTHER BRANCH SINCE VERSION 0.30. VERSIONS DEPENDING ON
           GTK1.2 AND SUPERMONGO WILL UNDERGO ONLY AND EXCLUSIVELY CRITI-
           CAL BUGFIXES, NO NEW FEATURES WILL BE ADDED. IF YOU WANT TO
           CONTRIBUTE, PLEASE READ THE TODO FILE IN THE TOPLEVEL PHOEBE
           VERSION 0.30 OR LATER.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                            ----------------------
                            | PHOEBE TO-DO LIST: |
                            ----------------------

configure.in, Makefile.am:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Add SM devices installation script to Makefile.am.

Keyword Files:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Add simpler routines for value readouts from keyword files.

Configuration:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Check whether chosen directories contain appropriate content.

Data Tab:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Add file format check when LC/RV data files are inputed in Data tab.
* Add experimental standard deviation calculation if possible.
* Support RV data files that contain normalized RV points (to orbit).

Basic Tab:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix PERIOD and HJD0 entries -> they must be in double precision and still
  be inputed as spin buttons. At least add validity check for input values.

Orbit Tab:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix DPERDT and DPDT entries -> they must be in double precision and still
  be inputed as spin buttons. At least add validity check for input values.

Luminosities Tab:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Add 3D animation of the binary.

Plotting:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Zooming doesn't work with big numbers. Check out what's wrong.
* Zooming and shifting is poorly done. Get rid of global variables and avoid lc
  calculation.
* Think how to enhance JD plots.
* Think how to plot multiple curves on one plot. Scrolls?
* Derivatives of r_pole ... r_back are still missing in plot info.
* Add error-bars possibility for experimental values based on weight and sigma.

Fitting:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Create a before/after picture so the user may compare the before/after
  solution.
* In case of DC divergence the output is poor. Enhance it.
* Move populate_dc_parameters_info_list from callbacks.
* DC info list should contain DC steps as well. Add them.
* User might want to perform multiple DC iterations. Support that.

MMS:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix the GUI. It looks and feels awful!

Limb Darkening:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Finish "Update All" callback function in LD interpolation.
* A long term plan could be to implement numerical integration of the monochro-
  matic LD tables. That way it would be possible (and easy) to add any new fil-
  ter with known bandpass properties; the only thing that would have to be sup-
  plied is the transmission function.

Synthetic grids:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Separate this part of code from callbacks to separate files and enhance their
  implementation. For now they remain disabled within PHOEBE.

Aliasing:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* If the basic interval is different than [-0.5, 0.5], aliasing doesn't work
  correctly.

Chi2 Calculation:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Add extrapolation support for points that fall out of synthetic phases range.

Chi2 Plotting:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Add RV chi2 plotting support.
* Add a switch to make the plot transparent (e.g. use 2 instead of 3 in the
  surface plotting function). Rethink the outlook of this GUI part.
* Add the option of rotating the plot in all three dimensions quickly.
* Add automatic boundary limits calculation (e.g. 10% +/- from the currently
  adopted value or sth like that).
* Add coloring of contour plots.

Programming Enhancements:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Calculate optimal RV VUNIT and use it internally.
* Optimize the numbering scheme for LCI/LCO files.
* Add undo support.
* Add debugging (mtrace, mcheck) and error-handling.

Visual Enhancements:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Add icons to a button box and elsewhere.

Physical questions:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* How can we calculate L/Lsun from HLA, T, ...? Implement that.

Tutorial:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* WORK ON IT! :)
